#: src/pages/ChatPage.tsx
msgid "60-second setup: create an Incoming Webhook in Slack (one channel, one URL) and paste it here. The agent gains exactly one ability — posting messages to that channel; it reads nothing from Slack. The URL stays in this tab's memory."
